--- In nbwrpg@y..., "dcoburn" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra/Composer::
> 
>     Orchestra listened to what Chameleon had to say.  Orchestra 
didn't need to tape record this, he had the best memory, for his 
function.
> 
>      "I see.  And you say everybody calls you a coward?  Don't 
worry about it....Nobody's a coward, sometimes they just aren't fit 
for fighting," Orchestra said slowly, holding back a tear or two from 
thinking of his brother Symphony, who never fought.  
> 
>        Orchestra turned back his attention to Chameleon.  Orchestra 
got himself a drink of energin, sipped, then continued talking.
> 
>       "Well, I must get going, gotta see Darkfate," Orchestra said.
> 
>       Orchestra walked out of the room.  He turned off the tape 
recorder.  Orchestra arrived to where Darkfate was.
> 
>       "Here's what I managed to get out of Chameleon," Orchestra 
said, handing the tape recorder to Darkfate.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>       Composer looked at Wheeljack.
> 
>       "Hey, I'm sure Zardus will allow us to go fight, besides, I 
would like to meet these Maximals," Composer said.
